{"tid":881534,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一件諗返起覺得dum春既事","createTime":"2018-10-29T13:36:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-19T03:25:45.000Z","uid":30100,"like":1,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"9465593d291b2f17ae581f85b27f41a7cca06b8b","tid":881534,"uid":30100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T13:36:11.000Z","msg":"小學二年班既時候係學校附近執到隻BB貓 應該2個月左右大<br />\n個時咩都唔識 又冇能力<br />\n<br />\n雖然帶左佢返屋企<br />\n但因為阿媽唔中意貓，同埋BB貓需求好大<br />\n佢又有啲肚痾既情況<br />\n一時之間又唔知帶佢去邊睇醫生<br />\n又唔識買野俾佢食<br />\n<br />\n個晚阿媽就搵條繩，輕輕綁住佢等佢唔好周圍走，同俾左啲水佢飲<br />\n因為佢可能唔舒服+肚餓，成晚不停咁叫<br />\n<br />\n第二日返學阿媽堅持要我帶返隻貓返去放生佢<br />\n唔準我養<br />\n我又唔知點算好 又冇經濟能力<br />\n唯有照做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n諗返起覺得好dum春<br />\n個下應該堅持(雖然應該都冇用)<br />\n自己明明好中意貓 依家就一隻都養唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n應該係個天懲罰緊我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"294a25b7e0729da59166fec3c316c276938231a4","tid":881534,"uid":147454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T13:41:26.000Z","msg":"有同事識個朋友係某殼股創業板公司主席<br />\n貨源歸哂邊，等緊時機炒上<br />\n佢同我講叫我買dd ，放一年<br />\n我買得兩萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，大半年最後賺左50%走人<br />\n<br />\n我老婆就屌7 我有內幕料先買得兩萬係咪on9"},{"pid":"2b2d4ce96c3dea386aa9c82a417c99f346e0cc81","tid":881534,"uid":30100,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"294a25b7e0729da59166fec3c316c276938231a4","tid":881534,"uid":147454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTi